      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nOverall Build Status: SUCCESS\n\nBuilder CentOS 6.7 x86_64 (BUILD) succeeded (build successful) - http://build.lustre.org/builders/CentOS%206.7%20x86_64%20%28BUILD%29/builds/13426\n\nBuilder CentOS 6.8 x86_64 (BUILD) succeeded (build successful) - http://build.lustre.org/builders/CentOS%206.8%20x86_64%20%28BUILD%29/builds/9562\n\nBuilder CentOS 7.2 x86_64 (BUILD) succeeded (build successful) - http://build.lustre.org/builders/CentOS%207.2%20x86_64%20%28BUILD%29/builds/13412\n\nBuilder Ubuntu 14.04 x86_64 (BUILD) succeeded (build successful) - http://build.lustre.org/builders/Ubuntu%2014.04%20x86_64%20%28BUILD%29/builds/13372",
